text: Apple M1 Max is a system-on-a-chip that was released on 18 Oct 2021. It has 57 billion transistors and 10 cores. It is used for 16-inch MacBook Pro (2021). It has a clock speed of 3.22GHz. == References == Category:64-bit Apple silicon Category:Processors released in 2020s Category:Multi-core processors
title: Apple M1 Max
